==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Gatling gun
<hw>Gat"ling gun`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>. <ety>[From the inventor, R.J.
<ets>Gatling</ets>.]</ety> <def>An American machine gun, consisting of a
cluster of barrels which, being revolved by a crank, are automatically
loaded and fired.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><note>⟦hand⟧ The improved <xex>Gatling gun</xex> can be fired at the
rate of 1,200 shots per minute.</note> <rj><au>Farrow.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>GATT</ent>⟦br⟧
